title: It‘s Holding You Back, Let it Go
itunes:title: It‘s Holding You Back, Let it Go
description:
Episode 586 - What tough things have you been through in your life? Do you wear them like a badge of honor, proudly displaying them for all to see? It's time to let go of them and realize that you are holding on to what is really holding you back. In this episode, I am going to dive into this topic and teach you how to create a new story.
